('dc6e2188-eff3-57fb-b1ff-b2b7c9b68599', 3, 'successor_check_live_fetch', 'positive', NULL, 'Live team page at https://www.vannoyassoc.com/ (fetched 2026-05-16). vannoyassoc.com (live-fetch 2026-05-16): Ray Lynn Vannoy RPLS #1988 (licensed 1978); services include boundary surveying, oil/gas surveys, pipeline surveys, easements/ROW, riparian boundaries, litigation/expert testimony, TX General Land Office matters, golf course surveys, consultation/training. NO drone/RTK/scanning/3D mention. Single Leander TX office. Cell phone (903) 574-1313 + Email Ray@vannoyassoc.com — extremely personal-direct contact.', 'live_website_fetch', 'https://www.vannoyassoc.com/', '2026-05-16'),
('dc6e2188-eff3-57fb-b1ff-b2b7c9b68599', 1, 'a_tier_deep_dive_completed', 'negative', NULL, 'Deep-dive outcome: demote_a_to_b. Items checked: 1_owner_age: Ray Vannoy ~78 (RPLS 1978 + ~30 age at license + ~18 years = 78). License-tenure proxy only; OV65 not verified.; 2_successor_verification: FAILED — Kalvin Walker is President of surveying operations per cross-referenced search results; not just an associate but the operating principal. Internal-succession in place.; 3_comptroller_status: Unverified via direct CAD/Comptroller lookup; firm shows active operations (3 offices, current website, current LinkedIn).; 4_disciplinary: No disciplinary action surfaced.; 5_civil_filings: None surfaced in search.; 6_building_ownership: Not verified.; 7_value_add_thesis: Multi-office + oil/gas + pipeline + litigation = specialty book is valuable, but the Walker succession in place means an outside buyer competes with internal-buy-out.; 8_metro_pull: Multi-office TX = broad exposure; not metro-pull-recomputed.', 'phase_5_a_tier_deep_dive', NULL, '2026-05-16'),
('f8e9d4e9-7cb7-591f-9d6a-91131d51829b', 1, 'owner_age_proxy_rpls_tenure', 'positive', NULL, 'Senior RPLS MURRAY BASS (TBPELS license #2128) granted 1979-12-07 → 47yr tenure. TX RPLS requires 4yr college + 4yr supervised survey-in-training + state exam (typically earned at age 28-35); est. owner age ~77.', 'tbpels_rpls_roster', 'https://tbpedownloads.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rpls_roster.csv', '2026-05-16'),
('f8e9d4e9-7cb7-591f-9d6a-91131d51829b', 2, 'firm_tenure_long', 'positive', NULL, 'Senior RPLS MURRAY BASS tenure 47yr per TBPELS RPLS roster. Firm registered as TBPELS Surveying Firm #10002700 since 2007-10-22. Passes >5yr settled-business hard gate.', 'tbpels_surveying_firms_roster', 'https://tbpedownloads.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/sur-firm_roster.csv', '2026-05-16'),
('f8e9d4e9-7cb7-591f-9d6a-91131d51829b', 2, 'rpls_license_skilled_trade_moat', 'positive', NULL, 'TX RPLS license = 4yr ABET-accredited surveying or equivalent + 4yr supervised survey-in-training + Tex. Occ. Code Ch. 1071 state exam. ~3,700 active RPLS statewide (TBPELS roster May 2026). Workforce documented as aging (TSPS workforce-shortage reports cite avg RPLS age >55).', 'tbpels_rpls_roster_aggregate', 'https://pels.texas.gov/roster/ls_rosters.html', '2026-05-16'),
('f8e9d4e9-7cb7-591f-9d6a-91131d51829b', 3, 'two_rpls_peer_aged', 'positive', NULL, '2 active RPLS at firm #10002700 but peer-aged (granted 0yr apart). No younger successor pipeline visible at license-board level.', 'tbpels_firm_rpls_join', 'https://tbpedownloads.s3-us-west-2.amazonaws.com/rpls_roster.csv', '2026-05-16'),
('f8e9d4e9-7cb7-591f-9d6a-91131d51829b', 4, 'low_pe_attention_vertical', 'positive', NULL, 'TX land surveying = LOW-PE-ATTENTION vertical. Only Bowman Consulting (NASDAQ:BWMN) + Westwood Professional Services (Endeavour Capital) are PE-backed rollup platforms active in TX surveying. Large-AEC strategics (Stantec/WSP/AECOM/Kimley-Horn/Cobb Fendley/LJA) only bolt-on $5M+ rev firms. Sub-$5M independent universe (Corpus Christi, Nueces County) structurally under-targeted = opportunity zone. ETA/search-fund appetite emerging fast 2024-2026 per Stanford Search Fund Study (top-15 ETA vertical).', 'verticals.md skill config + Stanford Search Fund Study + Bowman 10-K filings', 'https://pels.texas.gov/roster/ls_rosters.html', '2026-05-16'),
('f8e9d4e9-7cb7-591f-9d6a-91131d51829b', 3, 'enriched_coasting_tell', 'positive', NULL, 'Mid-size ($1M-$5M rev) two-partner firm in Corpus Christi — coastal/marine specialty niche.', 'enrichment', 'http://www.bass-welsh.com/', '2026-05-16'),
